{"type":null,"faqId":24704,"title":"电池无法正常充电，怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <a name=\"gen-id1.1.5.2.1.1.1\"></a><span>若电池电量完全耗尽，请连接充电器等待五分钟后查看是否恢复正常。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <a name=\"gen-id1.1.5.2.1.2.1\"></a><span>请尽量使用标配充电器充电。若使用标配充电器仍然充电失败，请重新插拔 USB 线、更换插线板或重启荣耀 X2。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <a name=\"gen-id1.1.5.2.1.3.1\"></a><span>荣耀 X2温度过高或过低时可能无法正常充电。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"gen-id1.1.5.2.1.3.2\"></a><span>荣耀 X2中有特有的温度保护设计，当荣耀 X2温度过高或过低时，会停止充电功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <a name=\"gen-id1.1.5.2.1.4.1\"></a><span>充电时请不要进行玩游戏、看视频、上网等大功耗的操作，在部分大功耗场景下，会增加充电时间，甚至出现电量减少现象。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>若问题依然存在，请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span>\n</p>\n<br>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":165,"faqType":"电池与充电","useful":1,"unUseful":4,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8704","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Battery-Charging","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1430104339000,"seriesProductName":"GEM-703L","visitedTimes":411,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"3","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"电池,充电,充不进去,充不了点","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}